comment: General version of ~ zfauscl , removing dependency on ~ ax-12 and ~ df-clab (and ~ df-tru , ~ df-sb , ~ df-v ). Remark: the comment in ~ zfauscl is misleading: the essential use of ~ ax-ext is the one via ~ eleq2 and not the one via ~ vtocl , since the latter can be proved without ~ ax-ext (see ~ bj-vtoclg ). (Contributed by BJ, 2-Jul-2022.) (Proof modification is discouraged.)
